<article class="row post">
  <header class="col-xs-12 media">
    <div class="media-left">
      <%= link_to image_tag('user_silhouette_generic.png', class: 'img-thumbnail media-object', alt: 'Generic User Image') %>
    </div>
    <div class="media-body">
      <h5 class="media-heading"><%= link_to post.user.first_name, user_about_path(post.user) %></h5>
      <p class="small text-muted"><%= post.date %></p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <p><%= post.body %></p>
  </div>
  <footer class="post-footer col-xs-12">
    <span class="post-action"><a href="#">Unlike</a></span>
    <span class="pull-right"><%= link_to "Delete", user_post_path(post.user, post), method: :delete, data: {confirm: 'Are you sure you want to delete this post?'} if is_self? %></span>
    <div class="post-reaction">
      <span>You and <a href="#">Hermione Granger</a> and 3 others like this</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
  <div class="post-comments col-xs-12 post-footer">
    <article class="row post-comment">
      <div class="col-xs-12 media">
        <div class="media-left">
          <%= link_to image_tag('user_silhouette_generic.png', class: 'img-thumbnail media-object', alt: 'Generic User Image') %>
        </div>
        <div class="media-body">
          <span class="media-heading h5"><a href="#">Ron Weasley</a></span>
          <span class="small text-muted">Posted on Thursday <time datetime="2014-6-1">6/1/2014</time></span>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repudiandae commodi, iste. Voluptatibus enim similique velit adipisci dolore reprehenderit qui! Veniam quod nisi, quia voluptas assumenda tenetur perspiciatis modi sunt animi.</p>
          <footer>
            <span class="post-action"><a href="#">Like</a><a href="#">Comment</a></span>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    
    <article class="row post-comment">
      <div class="col-xs-12 media">
        <div class="media-left">
          <%= link_to image_tag('user_silhouette_generic.png', class: 'img-thumbnail media-object', alt: 'Generic User Image') %>
        </div>
        <div class="media-body">
          <span class="media-heading h5"><a href="about.html">Harry Potter</a></span>
          <span class="small">Posted on Thursday <time datetime="2014-6-1">6/1/2014</time></span>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repudiandae commodi, iste. Voluptatibus enim similique velit adipisci dolore reprehenderit qui! Veniam quod nisi, quia voluptas assumenda tenetur perspiciatis modi sunt animi.</p>
          <footer>
            <span class="post-action"><a href="#">Like</a><a href="#">Comment</a><span><span class="text-muted">3 other people like this</span><span class="pull-right"><a href="#">Delete</a></span>
          </span></span></footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
  <form class="col-xs-12 form-group comment-form">
    <textarea name="comment" id="" cols="30" rows="2" class="form-control" placeholder="Write a comment"></textarea>
    <span><a href="#">Cancel</a></span>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary pull-right">Comment</button>
  </form>
</article>